== Research

My research is in the areas of system theory, signal processing, and control. Its distinct feature is using behavioral approach, developed 40 years ago by Jan C. Willems, see the [https://imarkovs.github.io/publications/overview-ddctr.pdf 2021 ARC overview paper] and the [https://imarkovs.github.io/book/book2e-2x1.pdf 2019 Springer monograph]. Technical keywords related to my research are:
~~~
{}{img_left}{erc-logo.gif}{ERC logo}{75px}{75px}{}
- [http://slra.github.io structured low-rank approximation and completion,]
- data-driven signal processing and control, and 
- system identification.
~~~

